description: If any of you Phoenicians are feelin’ cheesy, this funky truck is just for you. This gifted team is grilling up a tasty selection of crunchy, melty masterpieces that are sure to please; such as the Freebird with sharp cheddar cheese, roasted turkey breast, crispy bacon, sliced tomatoes, and the Hungry Hippie with BBQ Pork Mac & Cheese. For all this and more, c’mon out and check out this one-stop-shop for all things Cheese, Love & Happiness.
name: Cheese, Love & Happiness
